FBIS4-36570 "drnes112_j_94003" FBIS-NES-94-112 Daily Report 9 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Southern Military Source Says Air Raid Killed 5 Southern Military Source Says Air Raid Killed 5 EA0906165394 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 9 Jun 94 EA0906165394 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 9 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Excerpt] A responsible source at the Democratic Republic of Yemen Defense Ministry has issued the following statement to the YEMENI NEWS AGENCY, Aden: Four fighter aircraft belonging to the military ruling regime in Sanaa at 1200 raided a number of vital economic installations and residential quarters in Aden Governorate, destroying a number of houses belonging to innocent citizens. Five citizens were martyred, including three children. Our air defenses fought back, shooting down one of the aircraft, which citizens witnessed falling into the Gulf of Aden. [passage omitted]
